            <hgroup>
                
                <h1 class="headline"><a data-omni-click="inherit" href="/culture/2014/09/riding-the-rails-with-a-newly-minted-amtrak-writer-in-residence/380727/">Riding the Rails with a Newly Minted Amtrak Writer-in-Residence</a></h1>
            </hgroup>
            
            
                <address class="byline">By
                <a href="/authors/jake-swearingen/" title="Jake Swearingen" data-omni-click="inherit">
