            <hgroup>
                
                <h2 class="kicker"><a data-omni-click="inherit" href="/departments/todays-best/">Today&#39;s Best</a></h2>
                
                <h1 class="headline"><a data-omni-click="inherit" href="/national/2014/09/five-best-wednesday-columns/380696/">Five Best Wednesday Columns </a></h1>
            </hgroup>
            
            
                <address class="byline">By
                <a href="/authors/david-ludwig/" title="David Ludwig" data-omni-click="inherit">
                <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
