            <hgroup>
                
                <h2 class="kicker"><a data-omni-click="inherit" href="/departments/2014-fall-tv-preview/">2014 Fall TV Preview</a></h2>
                
                <h1 class="headline"><a data-omni-click="inherit" href="/entertainment/2014/09/how-to-get-away-with-murder-will-either-be-a-success-for-shonda-rhimes-or-a-flop-for-pete-nowalk/380590/">'How to Get Away with Murder' Will Be Another Shonda Rhimes Success or a Pete Nowalk Failure</a></h1>
            </hgroup>
            
            
                <address class="byline">By
                <a href="/authors/kevin-okeeffe/" title="Kevin O'Keeffe" data-omni-click="inherit">
